    <span class="upd-promo__dot"></span>
    <span class="upd-promo__item">📦 Livraison offerte dès <strong>30€</strong></span>
    <span class="upd-promo__dot"></span>
    <span class="upd-promo__item">🎁 <strong>UBE10</strong> · -10% 1ère commande</span>
